      <span style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px"><span style="display:inline-block;width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:3px;background:#fde8e8;border:1px solid #f5c6cb;font-size:13px;line-height:18px;text-align:center">🔴</span>Duplicato</span>
